Function Get-oAffinityLabel{
	<#
		.SYNOPSIS
			This function retrieves the Affinity Label on an oVirt Server system.
		.DESCRIPTION
			This function retrieves the Affinity Label on a oVirt Server system.
			Returns a set of Affinity Labels that correspond to the filter criteria provided by the function parameters.
