			The Id(s) of Affinity Label(s)
		.PARAMETER Syncopate
			Switch to Syncopate (truncate/abridge) returned data set
		.PARAMETER oVirtServerName
			The Name of the target oVirt Server (Oracle Linux Virualtization Manager)(OLVM) system
		.PARAMETER CaseSensitive
			Switch to search Case Sensitive oAffinityLabel name(s)
		.PARAMETER BatchRetrieve
			Future Feature, inactive
		.EXAMPLE
			PS> Get-oAffinityLabel -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName -Name $oAffinityLabel
				Returns the oAffinityLabel(s) by provided Name
