				#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/unregistered_storage_domains_discover
		.PARAMETER CommitNetConfig
			Marks the network configuration as good and persists it inside the host.
			An API user commits the network configuration to persist a host network interface attachment or detachment, or persist the creation and deletion of a bonded interface.
			NOTE:  Networking configuration is only committed after the engine has established that host connectivity is not lost as a result of the configuration changes.
				If host connectivity is lost, the host requires a reboot and automatically reverts to the previous networking configuration.
		.PARAMETER CopyHostNetworks
