		.PARAMETER FenceAgentUserName
			The UserName to log in to the Fence Agent
		.PARAMETER FenceAgentPassword
			The Password to log in to the Fence Agent
		.PARAMETER FenceAgentPort
			The UDP Port number to connect to the Fence Agent
			The most common is 623
		.PARAMETER FenceAgentOptions
			Text field to add additional Fence Agent configuration options. I.e. "lanplus", "lanplus=1", "lanplus=true,auth=password"
		.PARAMETER FenceAgentId
			The Id of an existing Fence Agent to remove or reorder
		.PARAMETER PowerManagementProxyAction
