						Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
						$Method = "PUT"
						$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "fenceagents"}).href + '/' + $FenceAgentId
						$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
						$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
						TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{}
						IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
					}
				}
			}

			#$FQDN, might not be changeable
			#$KSMEnabled & $TransparentHugePageEnabled, Might be Cluster level settings, that are inherited only
			IF(($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('NewName')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Comment')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Description')) -OR $FQDN -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('OverrideDisplayAddress')) -OR $SPMPriority -OR $vGPUPlacement -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('OverrideDisplayAddress')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('DisablePolicyControlOfPowerManagement')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnablePowerManagement')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('KdumpIntegration')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('KSMEnabled')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('TransparentHugePageEnabled')) -OR $RootPassword){
				IF(($oHostObject.status -eq "up") -OR ($oHostObject.status -eq "maintenance")){
					#Don't do this (kernel changes), can cause reboot and subsequent failed boot
					#$oHostObjectOSSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{custom_kernel_cmdline = "vfio_iommu_type1.allow_unsafe_interrupts=1"}
					$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('NewName')){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "name" -Value $PSBoundParameters['NewName'] -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Comment')){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "comment" -Value $PSBoundParameters['Comment'] -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					#I don't see this in the returned data, nor in teh gui, but the docs say it is present, so including
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Description')){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "description" -Value $PSBoundParameters['Description'] -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					#I don't think this can be changed, only used to add host to oVirt
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host
					IF($FQDN){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "address" -Value $FQDN -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/vgpu_placement
					IF($vGPUPlacement){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "vgpu_placement" -Value $vGPUPlacement -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/spm
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('SPMPriority')){
						SWITCH(($PSBoundParameters['SPMPriority'])){
							{$_ -eq "Never"}{$SPMPriorityValue = -1}
							{$_ -eq "Low"}{$SPMPriorityValue = 2}
							{$_ -eq "Normal"}{$SPMPriorityValue = 5}
							{$_ -eq "High"}{$SPMPriorityValue = 7}
						}
						$SPMSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{priority = $SPMPriorityValue}
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "spm" -Value $SPMSpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/power_management
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('DisablePolicyControlOfPowerManagement')){
						$PMPSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{enabled = !$DisablePolicyControlOfPowerManagement}
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "automatic_pm_enabled" -Value $PMPSpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnablePowerManagement')){
						$EPMSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{enabled = $EnablePowerManagement}
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "power_management" -Value $EPMSpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/power_management/attributes/kdump_detection
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/kdump_status
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('KdumpIntegration')){
						$KDISpec = [PSCustomObject]@{enabled = $KdumpIntegration}
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "kdump_detection" -Value $KDISpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host/attributes/ksm
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/ksm
					# $XMLString = "<host><ksm><enabled>true</enabled></ksm></host>"
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('KSMEnabled')){
						$KSMSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{enabled = $KSMEnabled}
						#<merge_across_nodes>true</merge_across_nodes>
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "ksm" -Value $KSMSpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/host/attributes/transparent_huge_pages
					# $XMLString = "<host><transparent_hugepages><enabled>false</enabled></transparent_hugepages></host>"
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('TransparentHugePageEnabled')){
						$THPSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{enabled = $TransparentHugePageEnabled}
						Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "transparent_hugepages" -Value $THPSpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/display/attributes/allow_override
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('OverrideDisplayAddress')){
						IF($OverrideDisplayAddress -eq $True){
							IF($DisplayAddress){
								$ODASpec = [PSCustomObject]@{address = $DisplayAddress}
								Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "display" -Value $ODASpec -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
							}
						}ElseIF($OverrideDisplayAddress -eq $False){
							Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "display" -Value $Null -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
						}
					}
					
					#Doesn't work, likely only used for New-oHost
					#IF($RootPassword){Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name root_password -Value $RootPassword -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs}
					
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
					#$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "update"}).href
					$Uri = $oHostObject.Uid
					$Method = "PUT"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] settings can't be applied unless in PoweredON, and in Active or Maintenance Mode, current status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}

			#Activate
			#Needs status of "maintenance"
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/activate
			IF($PSBoundParameters['OperationalState'] -eq 'Activate'){
				#IF($oHostObject.status -eq "maintenance"){
				IF(@("error","initializing","install_failed","maintenance","non_operational","pending_approval","preparing_for_maintenance","reboot","unassigned") -contains $oHostObject.status){
					IF($PSBoundParameters['RunAsync'].IsPresent -eq $True){
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $True}
					}Else{
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $False}
					}
					Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName | Out-Null
					$Token = $(($oVirtConnections | ?{$_.Name -eq $oVirtServerName}).ExtensionData.access_token)
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "activate"}).href
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't be placed in Active Mode while in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
			
			#Needs status of "up"
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/deactivate
			IF($PSBoundParameters['OperationalState'] -eq 'Maintenance'){
				#IF($oHostObject.status -eq "up"){
				IF(@("connecting","error","initializing","install_failed","installing","kdumping","non_operational","pending_approval","reboot","unassigned","up") -contains $oHostObject.status){
					IF($PSBoundParameters['RunAsync'].IsPresent -eq $True){
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $True}
					}Else{
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $False}
					}
					Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName | Out-Null
					$Token = $(($oVirtConnections | ?{$_.Name -eq $oVirtServerName}).ExtensionData.access_token)
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "deactivate"}).href
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					IF($PSCmdlet.ShouldProcess("$($oHostObject.Name)" , "Place oHost in Maintenance Mode")){
						TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't be Placed in Maintenance Mode in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
			
			#reboot
			#Needs status of "maintenance"
			#IF($PSBoundParameters['Reboot'].IsPresent -eq $True){
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
			IF($PSBoundParameters['FencePowerAction'] -eq 'Reboot'){
				IF($oHostObject.status -eq "maintenance"){
					$oHostObjectPowerSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{fence_type = "reboot"}
					$oHostObjectPowerActionSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{action = $oHostObjectPowerSpecs}
					IF($PSBoundParameters['RunAsync'].IsPresent -eq $True){
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $True}
					}Else{
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $False}
					}
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('MaintenanceAfterFenceReboot')){
						IF($PSBoundParameters['MaintenanceAfterFenceReboot'] -eq $True){
							$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{maintenance_after_restart = $PSBoundParameters['MaintenanceAfterFenceReboot']}
						}
					}
					Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "fence_type" -Value "restart" -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/fence_type
					#("manual","restart","start","status","stop")
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $( $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token))"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "fence"}).href
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					IF($PSCmdlet.ShouldProcess("$oHostObject.Name" , "Reboot oHost")){
						TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't be Rebooted in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
			
			#PowerOff
			#Needs status of "maintenance"
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
			IF($PSBoundParameters['FencePowerAction'] -eq 'PowerOff'){
				IF($oHostObject.status -eq "maintenance"){
					$oHostObjectPowerSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{fence_type = "stop"}
					$oHostObjectPowerActionSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{action = $oHostObjectPowerSpecs}
					IF($PSBoundParameters['RunAsync'].IsPresent -eq $True){
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $true}
					}Else{
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $false}
					}
					Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "maintenance_after_restart" -Value $true -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "fence_type" -Value "stop" -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/fence_type
					#("manual","restart","start","status","stop")
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $( $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token))"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "fence"}).href
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					IF($PSCmdlet.ShouldProcess("$oHostObject.Name" , "PowerOFF oHost")){
						TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't be PoweredOFF in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
			
			#PowerOn
			#Needs status of "down"
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
			IF($PSBoundParameters['FencePowerAction'] -eq 'PowerOn'){
				IF($oHostObject.status -eq "down"){
					$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{}
					#I'm not even sure this works, the returned object shows enabled, but the state is not set to Maintenance
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
					IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('MaintenanceAfterPowerOn')){
						IF($PSBoundParameters['MaintenanceAfterPowerOn'] -eq $True){
							$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{maintenance_after_restart = $PSBoundParameters['MaintenanceAfterPowerOn']}
						}
					}
					Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name "fence_type" -Value "start" -InputObject $oHostObjectSpecs
					#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/fence_type
					#("manual","restart","start","status","stop")
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $( $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token))"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "fence"}).href
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't be PoweredON in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
			
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/fence
			IF($PSBoundParameters['FencePowerStatus'].IsPresent -eq $True){
				$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{"fence_type"="status"}
				#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/fence_type
				#("manual","restart","start","status","stop")
				$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $( $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token))"; "All-Content"="true"}
				$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "fence"}).href
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri to Update oHost [$($Uri)]"
				$Method = "POST"
				$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oHost"
				Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
				$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
				TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
				IF($UpdatedoHostObject){Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$UpdatedoHostObject [$($UpdatedoHostObject | Out-String)]"; $OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				IF(!($WebError)){Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $oHostObject.oVirtServer}
			}
			
			#Power Management Proxy Preference, (What powerstate/status is needed?)
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/pm_proxy
			IF(($PSBoundParameters['PowerManagementProxyAction'])){
				$Uri = $oHostObject.Uid
				$CurrentProxyTypes = (Get-oUri -Uri $Uri).power_management.pm_proxies.pm_proxy.type
				$PowerManagementProxyArray = [System.Collections.ArrayList]@()
				IF(($PSBoundParameters['PowerManagementProxyAction']) -eq "add"){
					#Add Power Management Proxy
					ForEach($Item in $CurrentProxyTypes){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $Item){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $Item})) | Out-Null)}}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy1){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy1){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy1})) | Out-Null)}}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy2){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy2){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy2})) | Out-Null)}}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy3){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy3){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy3})) | Out-Null)}}
				}ElseIF(($PSBoundParameters['PowerManagementProxyAction']) -eq "remove"){
					#Remove Undefined Power Management Proxies
					IF($PowerManagementProxy1){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy1){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy1})) | Out-Null)}}Else{($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $CurrentProxyTypes[0]})) | Out-Null)}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy2){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy2){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy2})) | Out-Null)}}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy3){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy3){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy3})) | Out-Null)}}
				}ElseIF(($PSBoundParameters['PowerManagementProxyAction']) -eq "reorder"){
					#Update Power Management Proxy
					IF($PowerManagementProxy1){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy1})) | Out-Null)}Else{($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $CurrentProxyTypes[0]})) | Out-Null)}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy2){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy2){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy2})) | Out-Null)}}Else{IF($CurrentProxyTypes.Count -ge 2){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $CurrentProxyTypes[1]){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $CurrentProxyTypes[1]})) | Out-Null)}}}
					IF($PowerManagementProxy3){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $PowerManagementProxy3){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $PowerManagementProxy3})) | Out-Null)}}Else{IF($CurrentProxyTypes.Count -ge 3){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $CurrentProxyTypes[2]){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $CurrentProxyTypes[2]})) | Out-Null)}}}
					ForEach($Item in $CurrentProxyTypes){IF($PowerManagementProxyArray.type -NotContains $Item){($PowerManagementProxyArray.Add(([PSCustomObject]@{type = $Item})) | Out-Null)}}
				}
				$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{pm_proxy = $PowerManagementProxyArray}
				$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{pm_proxies = $oHostObjectSpecs}
				$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{power_management = $oHostObjectSpecs}
				$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to update oHost Power Management Proxy"
				Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
				$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
				$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $((Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName).ExtensionData.access_token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
				$Method = "PUT"
				TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{}
				IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
			}
			
			#Needs status of "up", "maintenance"
			#https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/host/methods/commit_net_config
			IF($PSBoundParameters['CommitNetConfig'].IsPresent -eq $True){
				IF(($oHostObject.status -eq "up") -OR ($oHostObject.status -eq "maintenance")){
					IF($PSBoundParameters['RunAsync'].IsPresent -eq $True){
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $True}
					}Else{
						$oHostObjectSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{async = $False}
					}
					Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName | Out-Null
					$Token = $(($oVirtConnections | ?{$_.Name -eq $oVirtServerName}).ExtensionData.access_token)
					$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
					$Uri = $BaseURL + ($oHostObject.actions.link | ?{$_.rel -eq "commitnetconfig"}).href
					$Method = "POST"
					$JsonBody = $oHostObjectSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to update oHost"
					Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
					$UpdatedoHostObject = $Null; $WebError = $Null
					IF($PSCmdlet.ShouldProcess("$oHostObject.Name" , "Commit Network Configuration to oHost [$($oHostObject.Name)]")){
						TRY{$UpdatedoHostObject = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$UpdatedoHostObject = $oHostObject}
					}
					IF($UpdatedoHostObject){$OutPutItems += $UpdatedoHostObject}
				}Else{Write-Warning "oHost [$($oHostObject.name)] can't Commit Network Configuration in status [$($oHostObject.status)]"}
			}
		}
	}
	End{
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$OutPutItems [$($OutPutItems | Out-String)]"; 
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$OutPutItems.count [$($OutPutItems.count)]"; 
		IF($OutPutItems.Count -gt 1){$(IF($OutPutItems.oVirtServer){$OutPutItems | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_} ; $OutPutItems})}ElseIF($OutPutItems.Count -eq 1){$(IF(($OutPutItems[0]).oVirtServer){$OutPutItems[0] | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}; $OutPutItems[0])}
	}
}

Function Set-oMacPool{
	<#
		.SYNOPSIS
			This function updates an oMacPool, on an oVirt Server system.
		.DESCRIPTION
			This function updates an oMacPool, on a oVirt Server system.
			Returns the job response from the oVirt Server.
		.PARAMETER Name
			The Name(s) of the oMacPool(s)
			Can use Wildcard '*'
		.PARAMETER Id
			The Id(s) of the oMacPool(s)
		.PARAMETER Uid
			The Uid of the oMacPool(s)
		.PARAMETER oVirtServerName
			The Name of the target oVirt Server (Oracle Linux Virualtization Manager)(OLVM) system
		.PARAMETER NewName
			The New Name for the oMacPool
		.PARAMETER Description
			The Text for the Description field to set on the oMacPool
		.PARAMETER AllowDuplicates
			Defines whether duplicate MAC addresses are permitted in the pool.
		.PARAMETER DefaultPool
			Defines whether this is the default pool.
		.PARAMETER FromMacAddress
			Starting MAC address in new oMacPool
		.PARAMETER ToMacAddress
			Ending MAC address in new oMacPool
		.PARAMETER oVirtServerName
			The Name of the target oVirt Server (Oracle Linux Virualtization Manager)(OLVM) system
		.PARAMETER RunAsync
			Execute a task asynchronously (without waiting for completion), and return a task instead of the regular output
		.EXAMPLE
			PS> Set-oMacPool -Name "MyoMacPool" -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName -Description "ForVDIs" -FromMacAddress "00:00:00:00:00:00" -ToMacAddress "11-11-11-11-11-11"
				Updates an oMacPool
		.INPUTS
			[System.String]
			[oMacPool]
		.OUTPUTS
			[System.String]
			[PSCustomObject]
			[oMacPool]
		.NOTES
			See David A. Stewart <itsavant@gmail.com>.
			Version 1.0		12/18/2024
		.LINK
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/mac_pool
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/mac_pool
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/mac_pools
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/mac_pool/methods/update
		.LINK
			See David A. Stewart <david.a.stewart@Oracle.com>.
		.LINK
			New-oMacPool
			Get-oMacPool
			Remove-oMacPool
			Get-Help
	#>
	[CmdletBinding(SupportsShouldProcess, ConfirmImpact = 'High', DefaultParameterSetName = 'Set01')]
	Param(
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$True, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set01", Position=0)]
			[ValidateScript({($_).GetType().Name -match 'oMacPool|String'})]$Name,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$True, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set02")]
			[ValidatePattern('^[0-9a-zA-Z]{8}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{12}$')]
			[System.String]$Id,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$True, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set03")]
			[ValidateScript({IF(([Uri]$_).AbsoluteUri -eq $Null){Throw [System.Management.Automation.ValidationMetadataException] "The input Uid: `'${_}`' is not a valid Uid"}Else{$True}})]
			[System.String]$Uid,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[System.String]$NewName,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[System.String]$Description,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$AllowDuplicates,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[SWITCH]$DefaultPool,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[ValidatePattern('^([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}[:-]){5}([0-9A-Fa-f]{2})|([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}){6}$')]
			[System.String]$FromMacAddress,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[ValidatePattern('^([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}[:-]){5}([0-9A-Fa-f]{2})|([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}){6}$')]
			[System.String]$ToMacAddress,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[SWITCH]$RunAsync,
		
		#oVirtServerName
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True,  HelpMessage="oVirtServerName (Name or IP)")]
			[Alias('oVirtServer')]
			[System.String]$oVirtServerName
	)
	Begin{
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Running"
		IF($oVirtServerName){
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
		}Else{
			$oVirtServerName = $oVirtConnections[0].oVirtServerName
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
		}
	}
	Process{
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) Parameter Set: [$($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName)]"
		Write-Verbose "Parameter Set: [$($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName)]"
		$oMacPoolObject = $Null
		IF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set01"){
			SWITCH($PSBoundParameters['Name']){
				{$_ -IS [System.String]}{
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oMacPool is String"
					IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
						$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
					}Else{
						$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -EA SilentlyContinue
					}
					IF($oMacPoolObject){$oMacPoolObject | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
				}
				{$_.GetType().Name -eq "String"}{
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oMacPool GetType equals String"
					IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
						$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
					}Else{
						$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -EA SilentlyContinue
					}
					IF($oMacPoolObject){$oMacPoolObject | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
				}
				{$_ -IS [oMacPool]}{
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) Name is [oMacPool]"
					$oMacPoolObject = $PSBoundParameters['Name']
				}
				{$_.GetType().Name -eq "oMacPool"}{
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) Name GetType equals [oMacPool]"
					$oMacPoolObject = $PSBoundParameters['Name']
				}
				DEFAULT{
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) DEFAULT TYPE SECTION"
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oMacPool is GetType: $($_.GetType() | Out-String)"
					Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) `$_: $($_ | Out-String)"
				}
			}
		}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set02"){
			IF($PSBoundParameters['Id']){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
					$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Id $PSBoundParameters['Id'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
				}Else{
					$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Id $PSBoundParameters['Id'] -EA SilentlyContinue
				}
				IF($oMacPoolObject){$oMacPoolObject | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
			}
		}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set03"){
			IF($PSBoundParameters['Uid']){
				$UidUrl = [Uri]$Uid
				$oMacPoolObject = Get-oMacPool -Id ($UidUrl.Segments[($UidUrl.Segments.count -1)]) -oVirtServerName ($UidUrl.Host) -EA SilentlyContinue
				IF($oMacPoolObject){$oMacPoolObject | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
			}
		}
		
		IF($oMacPoolObject){
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$PSBoundParameters: [$($PSBoundParameters | Out-String)]"
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$oMacPoolObject Names: $($oMacPoolObject.Name)"
			$OutPutItems = [System.Collections.ArrayList]@()
			
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$oMacPoolObject [$($oMacPoolObject | Out-String)]"
			$oVirtServerName = $oMacPoolObject.oVirtServer
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
			
			$oMacPoolSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('NewName')){ $oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'name' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['NewName']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Description')){IF($PSBoundParameters['Description']){$oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'description' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['Description'])}}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('AllowDuplicates')){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['AllowDuplicates'] -eq $True){$oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'allow_duplicates' -Value $True}Else{$oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'allow_duplicates' -Value $False}
			}
			IF(($PSBoundParameters['DefaultPool'].IsPresent -eq $True)){$oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'default_pool' -Value $True}
			
			IF(($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('FromMacAddress')) -OR ($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('ToMacAddress'))){
				$oMacPoolRangeSpec = [PSCustomObject]@{}
				IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('FromMacAddress')){ $oMacPoolRangeSpec | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'from' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['FromMacAddress']) }
				IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('ToMacAddress')){ $oMacPoolRangeSpec | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'to' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['ToMacAddress']) }
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$oMacPoolRangeSpec: [$($oMacPoolRangeSpec | Out-String)]"
				IF($oMacPoolRangeSpec){$oMacPoolSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'ranges' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'range'=([ARRAY]@($oMacPoolRangeSpec))})}
			}

			#Send to Server
			Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName | Out-Null
			$Token = $(($oVirtConnections | ?{$_.Name -eq $oVirtServerName}).ExtensionData.access_token)
			$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
			#$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/xml";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
			$Uri = $BaseURL + "/ovirt-engine/api/macpools/$($oMacPoolObject.id)"
			$Method = "PUT"
			$JsonBody = $oMacPoolSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
			#$JsonBody | ConvertFrom-Json2Xml
			#($oMacPoolSpecs | ConvertTo-Json | ConvertFrom-Json2Xml)
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oMacPool"
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$Uri: [$($JsonBody)]"
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): $($JsonBody | Out-String)"
			$UpdatedoMacPool = $Null
			TRY{$UpdatedoMacPool = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$FormattedWebError = (Format-WebError -WebError $WebError -Body $JsonBody -Uri $Uri); $OutPutItems.Add($FormattedWebError) | Out-Null; Write-Error $FormattedWebError}
			IF($UpdatedoMacPool){
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Updated oMacPool"
				$OutPutItems.Add((Convert-RestResponseTooVirtObject -InputObject $UpdatedoMacPool -ObjectType "oMacPool" -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName)) | Out-Null
				Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName
			}Else{
				Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Error [$($WebError | Out-String)]"
			}
		}Else{
			$oMacPoolInputString = $Null
			IF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set01"){
				SWITCH($PSBoundParameters['Name']){
				{$_ -IS [System.String]}{$oMacPoolInputString = $PSBoundParameters['Name']}
				{$_.GetType().Name -eq "String"}{$oMacPoolInputString = $PSBoundParameters['Name']}
				{$_ -IS [oMacPool]}{$oMacPoolInputString = $PSBoundParameters['Name'].Name}
				{$_.GetType().Name -eq "oMacPool"}{$oMacPoolInputString = $PSBoundParameters['Name'].Name}
				}
			}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set02"){
				$oMacPoolInputString = $PSBoundParameters['Id']
			}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set03"){
				$oMacPoolInputString = ($UidUrl.Segments[($UidUrl.Segments.count -1)])
			}
			IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
				Write-Warning "Could not locate oMacPool by input [$($oMacPoolInputString)] on [$($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'])]"
			}Else{
				Write-Warning "Could not locate oMacPool by input [$($oMacPoolInputString)]"
			}
		}
	}
	End{Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): End"; IF($OutPutItems.Count -gt 1){$OutPutItems}ElseIF($OutPutItems.Count -eq 1){$OutPutItems[0]}}
}

Function Set-oNetwork{
	<#
		.SYNOPSIS
			This function reconfigures the provided oNetwork, on an oVirt Server system.
		.DESCRIPTION
			This function reconfigures the provided oNetwork, on a oVirt Server system.
			Returns the job response from the oVirt Server.
			The oVirt documentation online states all 3 lines.....
				Only the name, comment, description, and MTU can be changed.
				The name, description, ip, vlan, stp and display attributes can be updated.
				The maximum transmission unit of a network is set using a PUT request to specify the integer value of the mtu attribute.
		.PARAMETER Name
			The Name(s) of oNetwork(s)
			Can use Wildcard '*'
		.PARAMETER Id
			The Id(s) of oNetwork(s)
		.PARAMETER Uid
			The Uid(s) of oNetwork(s)
		.PARAMETER NewName
			The New Name to Assign the oNetwork
		.PARAMETER Comment
			The Text for the Comment field to set on the oNetwork
		.PARAMETER Description
			The Text for the Description field to set on the oNetwork
		.PARAMETER MTU
			The MTU (maximum transmission unit) for the oNetwork
				Default is 1500
				Valid range 68 to 65536
		.PARAMETER EnableVLANtagging
			Enables/Disables VLAN tagging
		.PARAMETER vLanId
			The vLAN Id to set if VLAN tagging is enabled
		.PARAMETER EnableVMNetwork
			Enables/Disables setting the Network to be used for VM traffic
		.PARAMETER Required
			Enables/Disables setting the Network to be required on all oHosts
			This Only works if the Network has been added to an oCluster
		.PARAMETER PortIsolation
			Enables/Disables blocking communication between VMs running on the same host on this network.
		.PARAMETER HostNetworkQoSId
			The Host Network QoS Id
			Default is "unlimited"
		.PARAMETER EnableDNSConfiguration
			Enables/Disables dedicated DNS configuration overriding inheritence
		.PARAMETER DNSServers
			The IP Address(es) and/or Name(s) of DNS server(s) for this network
		.PARAMETER STP
			Enables/Disables whether the spanning tree protocol is enabled for this network
		.PARAMETER oVirtServerName
			The Name of the target oVirt Server (Oracle Linux Virualtization Manager)(OLVM) system
		.EXAMPLE
			PS> Set-oNetwork -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName -NewName "Name" -MTU 9000 -Comment "Jumbo Frames Enabled"
				Changes the Name of the oNetwork(s) to the provided NewName
		.INPUTS
			[System.String]
			[oNetwork]
		.OUTPUTS
			[System.String]
			[PSCustomObject]
			[oNetwork]
		.NOTES
			See David A. Stewart <itsavant@gmail.com>.
			Version 1.0		6/7/2024
			Version 1.0b		8/6/2024
		.LINK
			See David A. Stewart <david.a.stewart@Oracle.com>.
		.LINK
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/networks
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#services/networks/methods/update
			https://ovirt.github.io/ovirt-engine-api-model/4.5/#types/network
			Get-Help
		.LINK
			Get-oNetwork
			New-oNetwork
			Remove-oNetwork
			Get-Help		
	#>
	[CmdletBinding(SupportsShouldProcess, ConfirmImpact = 'High', DefaultParameterSetName = 'Set01')]
	Param(
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$True, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set01", Position=0)]
			[ValidateScript({($_).GetType().Name -match 'String|oNetwork'})]$Name,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$True, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set02")]
			[ValidatePattern('^[0-9a-zA-Z]{8}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{4}-[0-9a-zA-Z]{12}$')][System.String]$Id,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$True, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True, ParameterSetName="Set03")]
			[ValidateScript({IF(([Uri]$_).AbsoluteUri -eq $Null){Throw [System.Management.Automation.ValidationMetadataException] "The input Uid: `'${_}`' is not a valid Uid"}Else{$True}})]
			[System.String]$Uid,
		[System.String]$NewName,
		[System.String]$Comment,
		[System.String]$Description,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[ValidateRange(68,65536)][INT32]$MTU,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$EnableVLANtagging,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[ValidateRange(1,4095)][INT32]$vLanId,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$EnableVMNetwork,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$Required,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$PortIsolation,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[ValidateScript({IF(([Uri]$_).AbsoluteUri -eq $Null){Throw [System.Management.Automation.ValidationMetadataException] "The input Uid: `'${_}`' is not a valid Uid"}Else{$True}})]
			[System.String]$HostNetworkQoSId,
		
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$EnableDNSConfiguration,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			#[ValidateScript({IF(() -or ()){$True}Else{Throw [System.Management.Automation.ValidationMetadataException] "The input: `'${_}`' is not a valid IP Address or FQDN"}})]
			[System.String[]]$DNSServers,
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$False)]
			[BOOLEAN]$STP,
		
		#oVirtServerName
		[Parameter(Mandatory=$False, ValueFromPipeline=$False, ValueFromPipelineByPropertyName=$True,  HelpMessage="oVirtServerName (Name or IP)")]
			[Alias('oVirtServer')]
			[System.String]$oVirtServerName
	)
	Begin{
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Running"
		IF($oVirtServerName){
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
		}Else{
			$oVirtServerName = $oVirtConnections[0].oVirtServerName
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
		}
	}
	Process{
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) Parameter Set: [$($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName)]"
		Write-Verbose "Parameter Set: [$($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName)]"
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) `$PSBoundParameters: [$($PSBoundParameters | Out-String)]"
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) Is [oNetwork]: [$($PSBoundParameters['Name'] -IS [oNetwork])]"
		IF($PSBoundParameters['Name']){Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) `$PSBoundParameters['Name'] Type: [$(($PSBoundParameters['Name']).GetType().Name)]"}
		$oNetworkObjects = $Null
		IF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set01"){
			IF($PSBoundParameters['Name']){
				SWITCH($PSBoundParameters['Name']){
					{$_ -IS [System.String]}{
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oNetwork is String"
						IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
							$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
						}Else{
							$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -EA SilentlyContinue
						}
						IF($oNetworkObjects){$oNetworkObjects | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
					}
					{$_.GetType().Name -eq "String"}{
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oNetwork GetType equals String"
						IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
							$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
						}Else{
							$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Name $PSBoundParameters['Name'] -EA SilentlyContinue
						}
						IF($oNetworkObjects){$oNetworkObjects | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
					}
					{$_ -IS [oNetwork]}{
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oNetwork is [oNetwork]"
						$oNetworkObjects = $PSBoundParameters['Name']
					}
					{$_.GetType().Name -eq "oNetwork"}{
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oNetwork GetType equals [oNetwork]"
						$oNetworkObjects = $PSBoundParameters['Name']
					}
					DEFAULT{
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) DEFAULT TYPE SECTION"
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) oNetwork is GetType: $($_.GetType() | Out-String)"
						Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand) `$_: $($_ | Out-String)"
					}
				}
			}
		}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set02"){
			IF($PSBoundParameters['Id']){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName']){
					$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Id $PSBoundParameters['Id'] -oVirtServerName $PSBoundParameters['oVirtServerName'] -EA SilentlyContinue
				}Else{
					$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Id $PSBoundParameters['Id'] -EA SilentlyContinue
				}
				IF($oNetworkObjects){$oNetworkObjects | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
			}
		}ElseIF($PSCmdlet.ParameterSetName -eq "Set03"){
			IF($PSBoundParameters['UId']){
				$UidUrl = [Uri]$Uid
				$oNetworkObjects = Get-oNetwork -Id ($UidUrl.Segments[($UidUrl.Segments.count -1)]) -oVirtServerName ($UidUrl.Host) -EA SilentlyContinue
				IF($oNetworkObjects){$oNetworkObjects | Select -Unique -ExpandProperty oVirtServer | Sort -Unique | %{Update-oVirtServer_LastUsedTime -oVirtServerName $_}}
			}
		}
		
		Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$oNetworkObjects Names: $($oNetworkObjects.Name)"
		$OutPutItems = [System.Collections.ArrayList]@()
		ForEach($oNetworkObject in $oNetworkObjects){
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): `$oNetworkObject [$($oNetworkObject | Out-String)]"
			$oVirtServerName = $oNetworkObject.oVirtServer
			$BaseURL = "https://$($oVirtServerName)"
			$oNetworkSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('NewName')){ $oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'name' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['NewName']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Comment')){ $oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'comment' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['Comment']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Description')){ $oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'description' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['Description']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('MTU')){ $oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'mtu' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['MTU']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('STP')){ $oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'stp' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['STP']) }
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnableVLANtagging')){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['EnableVLANtagging'] -eq $True){
					IF($PSBoundParameters['vLanId']){$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'vlan' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{"id"=$PSBoundParameters['vLANId']})}
				}Else{
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'vlan' -Value $null
					#The official documentation suggests using the above to remove a vlan, it is wrong, below is correct.
					$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'vlan' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{"id"=$null})
				}
			}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnableDNSConfiguration')){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['EnableDNSConfiguration'] -eq $True){
					IF($PSBoundParameters['DNSServers']){
						$NameServersSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{}
						ForEach($Item in $PSBoundParameters['DNSServers']){
							$DNSSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'name_server' -Value $Item
						}
						$NameServersSpecs = [PSCustomObject]@{"name_servers" = $NameServersSpecs}
						$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'dns_resolver_configuration' -Value $NameServersSpecs
					}
				}Else{
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'dns_resolver_configuration' -Value $Null
					$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'dns_resolver_configuration' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{"name_servers" = $([PSCustomObject]@{"name_server" = $null})})
				}
			}
			#IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnableVMNetwork')){IF($PSBoundParameters['EnableVMNetwork'] -eq $True){$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'="vm"})}}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('EnableVMNetwork')){
				IF($PSBoundParameters['EnableVMNetwork'] -eq $True){
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'="vm"})
					$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'=@("vm")})
				}Else{
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'="null"})
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'=""})
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $Null
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'=@("null")})
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'=@("")})
					#$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value @()
					$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'usages' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{'usage'=$null})
					
				}
			}
			IF($PSBoundParameters.ContainsKey('Required')){IF($PSBoundParameters['Required'] -eq $True){$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'required' -Value $($PSBoundParameters['Required'])}}
			IF($PSBoundParameters['HostNetworkQoSId']){$oNetworkSpecs | Add-Member -MemberType NoteProperty -Name 'qos' -Value $([PSCustomObject]@{"id"=$PSBoundParameters['HostNetworkQoSId']})}
			
			#Send to Server
			Resolve-oVirtConnection -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName | Out-Null
			$Token = $(($oVirtConnections | ?{$_.Name -eq $oVirtServerName}).ExtensionData.access_token)
			$Headers = @{"Accept" = "application/json";"Authorization" = "Bearer $($Token)"; "All-Content"="true"}
			$Uri = $BaseURL + "/ovirt-engine/api/networks/$($oNetworkObject.Id)"
			$Method = "PUT"
			$JsonBody = $oNetworkSpecs | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 50
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Submitting Json to Update oNetwork"
			Write-Verbose "$($JsonBody | Out-String)"
			Write-Verbose "$($MyInvocation.MyCommand): Uri: $($Uri | Out-String)"
			$UpdatedoNetwork = $Null
			TRY{$UpdatedoNetwork = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $Uri -Headers $Headers -Method $Method -Body $JsonBody -ContentType "application/json" -EV WebError}Catch{$FormattedWebError = (Format-WebError -WebError $WebError -Body $JsonBody -Uri $Uri); $OutPutItems.Add($FormattedWebError) | Out-Null; Write-Error $FormattedWebError}
			IF($UpdatedoNetwork){
				$OutPutItems.Add((Convert-RestResponseTooVirtObject -InputObject $UpdatedoNetwork -ObjectType "oNetwork" -oVirtServerName $oVirtServerName)) | Out-Null
			}
		}
	}
	End{IF($OutPutItems.Count -gt 1){$OutPutItems}ElseIF($OutPutItems.Count -eq 1){$OutPutItems[0]}}
}

