			The existing oAffinityGroup Id to update. Prefers parent oCluster also provided to reduce time searching inventory.
		.PARAMETER oAffinityGroupUid
			The existing oAffinityGroup Uid to update
		.PARAMETER oCluster
			The oCluster target parent of an existing oAffinityGroup
			Can be a text name or an [oCluster] PSObject
			Not Needed if [oAffinityGroup] PSObject is Provided
		.PARAMETER oClusterId
			The oCluster target Id parent of an existing oAffinityGroup
		.PARAMETER oClusterUid
			The oCluster target Uid parent of an existing oAffinityGroup
