			The oHost(s) to add/remove to/from an existing oAffinityGroup
			Can be a text name(s) or an [oHost] PSObject(s)
		.PARAMETER oHostId
			The oHost Id(s) to add/remove to/from an existing oAffinityGroup
		.PARAMETER oHostUid
			The oHost Uid(s) to add/remove to/from an existing oAffinityGroup
		.PARAMETER RemoveoHost
			Switch to REMOVE provided oHost(s) from an existing oAffinityGroup. Otherwise Adds provided oHost(s).
		.PARAMETER oHostLabel
