			Affinity groups with lower priority are more likely to be broken.
			Decimal number
		.PARAMETER HostAffinityRule (Disabled, Positive, Negative)
			oHost Polarity
			Specifies whether the affinity group applies positive affinity or negative affinity to KVM hosts that are members of that affinity group.
		.PARAMETER VMAffinityRule (Disabled, Positive, Negative)
			oVM Polarity
			Specifies whether the affinity group applies positive affinity or negative affinity to virtual machines that are members of that affinity group.
		.PARAMETER HostAffinityRuleEnforcing (True, False)
			Specifies whether the affinity group uses hard or soft enforcement of the affinity applied to KVM hosts that are members of that affinity group.
		.PARAMETER VMAffinityRuleEnforcing (True, False)
