		.PARAMETER oHostUid
			The Uid of the parent oHost for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
		.PARAMETER oHostNic
			The Name of the oHostNic for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
		.PARAMETER oHostNicId
			The Id of the oHostNic for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
		.PARAMETER oHostNicUid
			The Uid of the oHostNic for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
		.PARAMETER oNetwork
			The Name of the oNetwork for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
		.PARAMETER oNetworkId
			The Id of the oNetwork for the new oNetworkAttachment(s)
