Function Set-oVmNic{
	<#
		.SYNOPSIS
			This function reconfigures the provided oVmNic, on an oVirt Server system.
		.DESCRIPTION
			This function reconfigures the provided oVmNic, on a oVirt Server system.
			Returns the job response from the oVirt Server.
		.PARAMETER oVmNic
			The oVmNic Object
			Can use Wildcard '*'
				I.e. MyIte*
		.PARAMETER Uid
			The Uid(s) of oVmNic(s)
		.PARAMETER oVNicProfile
			The Name of the parent oVNicProfile for the new oVmNic(s)
		.PARAMETER oVNicProfileId
			The Id of the parent oVNicProfile for the new oVmNic(s)
		.PARAMETER oVNicProfileUid
			The Uid of the parent oVNicProfile for the new oVmNic(s)
		.PARAMETER oVirtServerName
			The Name of the target oVirt Server (Oracle Linux Virualtization Manager)(OLVM) system
		.PARAMETER Type
			The Type of the oVmNic
